Summary: Egg shaped UFO seen on Christmas day on the top of 72nd and Dodge Street, Omaha.
divs: Sighting DetailsEgg Shaped UFO was stationary right on top 72nd and dodge street, Omaha, NE. Since it was 11 pm, it too dark and before I could reach for my camera it was gone. But it was blinking 2 lights on each side ( left and right ) of an egg shaped UFO. It was vanished in a 15 seconds. Earlier it was moving very fast but it stopped on that street. Approx was at the height of 700km from earth and was forming an angle of 60 degree from my eye contact to that UFO. Hope this helps you !
